This is a simple demo of JSON using the Spoonacular API.

To use this repository, you must follow these steps:

0. Sign up for spoonacular at https://spoonacular.com/food-api/console.
1. Navigate to https://spoonacular.com/food-api/console#Profile and find your API Key (THIS IS SECRET, DO NOT SHOW THIS TO OTHERS!).
2. Clone this repository by using git clone.
3. In your local copy of this repository, create a new root-level file called spoonacular.env
4. Add the following line in spoonacular.env: 
    SPOONACULAR_KEY='your_key_here'
5. Run the following, where the brackets indicate optional changes to the command you may have to run:
    [sudo] [/path/to/]pip[3] install python-dotenv
6. Save spoonacular.env and run your python file.
